class KeyedException(Exception):
    
    def __init__(self, *args, path):
        super().__init__(*args)
        self.path = path

class ApplyKeyedException(KeyedException):
    
    def __init__(self, *args, path, value):
        super().__init__(*args, path=path)
        self.value = value
